<br>
That is based on board reading and the one time up there, so please test it and post here.<br>
<br>
As someone mentioned above the bottle size DOES seem to alter either the length of time between calls OR the number he calls with each wave.  I SWEAR with a small bottle we had at least one pull with 6 fungusbeasts around.  He was waiting 3 minutes between.<br>
<br>
Maybe I'm wrong and a small bottle = 4 creatures, medium is 5, and large is 6.<br>
<br>
/shrug<br>
